# 2. Prime Checking

Naive:

```cpp
bool isPrime(long long n){
    if(n < 2) return false;

    for(long long i = 2; i * i <= n; i++)
        if(n % i == 0)
            return false;

    return true;
}
```

Complexity:

```text
O(√n)
```

Must know.

