# 3. Sieve of Eratosthenes

Most important Number Theory template.

Find all primes up to N.

```cpp
const int N = 1000000;

vector<bool> prime(N+1,true);

void sieve(){

    prime[0] = prime[1] = false;

    for(int i = 2; i * i <= N; i++){

        if(prime[i]){

            for(int j = i*i; j <= N; j += i)
                prime[j] = false;
        }
    }
}
```

Complexity:

```text
O(N log log N)
```

