# 4. Prime Factorization

```cpp
vector<pair<long long,int>> factorize(long long n){

    vector<pair<long long,int>> f;

    for(long long p = 2; p * p <= n; p++){

        if(n % p == 0){

            int cnt = 0;

            while(n % p == 0){
                cnt++;
                n /= p;
            }

            f.push_back({p,cnt});
        }
    }

    if(n > 1)
        f.push_back({n,1});

    return f;
}
```

Example:

```text
360
=
2³ × 3² × 5
```

