# 5. GCD

Most used function in Number Theory.

Euclid:

\gcd(a,b)=\gcd(b,a\bmod b)

Code:

```cpp
long long gcd(long long a, long long b){

    while(b){

        long long r = a % b;

        a = b;
        b = r;
    }

    return a;
}
```

Or:

```cpp
gcd(a,b);
```

from STL.

