# 6. LCM

[
\text{lcm}(a,b)
===============

\frac{a\cdot b}{\gcd(a,b)}
]

\operatorname{lcm}(a,b)=\frac{ab}{\gcd(a,b)}

Code:

```cpp
long long lcm(long long a,long long b){
    return a / gcd(a,b) * b;
}
```

