# 7. Extended Euclid

Solves:

[
ax + by = gcd(a,b)
]

Template:

```cpp
long long ext_gcd(long long a,
                  long long b,
                  long long &x,
                  long long &y){

    if(b == 0){

        x = 1;
        y = 0;

        return a;
    }

    long long x1,y1;

    long long g =
        ext_gcd(b,a%b,x1,y1);

    x = y1;

    y = x1 - y1*(a/b);

    return g;
}
```

Needed for:

* Diophantine equations
* Modular inverse (non-prime mod)

