# 8. Euler's Totient

Very common.

[
\varphi(n)
==========

#{1\le x\le n:\gcd(x,n)=1}
]

Formula:

If

[
n=p_1^{a_1}p_2^{a_2}\cdots
]

then

[
\varphi(n)
==========

n
\prod
\left(1-\frac1p\right)
]

Code:

```cpp
long long phi(long long n){

    long long result = n;

    for(long long p=2; p*p<=n; p++){

        if(n%p==0){

            while(n%p==0)
                n/=p;

            result -= result/p;
        }
    }

    if(n>1)
        result -= result/n;

    return result;
}
```

