# 11. Modular Exponentiation

You already learned this.

```cpp
long long binpow(long long a,
                 long long b,
                 long long mod){

    long long res = 1;

    while(b){

        if(b&1)
            res = res*a%mod;

        a = a*a%mod;

        b >>= 1;
    }

    return res;
}
```

