# 15. Fast Divisor Enumeration

```cpp
vector<long long> divisors(long long n){

    vector<long long> d;

    for(long long i=1;i*i<=n;i++){

        if(n%i==0){

            d.push_back(i);

            if(i*i!=n)
                d.push_back(n/i);
        }
    }

    return d;
}
```

Complexity:

```text
O(√n)
```

